    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_3_402-434",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "402-434",
      "markText": "“拥有自己的人生，爱上真实的自己，这将是我们所做的最勇敢的事。”",
      "totalCount": 2839,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=402&rangeEnd=434",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=402&rangeEnd=434"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_3_2826-2864",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2826-2864",
      "markText": "若想全心投入生活，对自我的认识和了解程度至关重要，但比这更重要的是：爱自己。",
      "totalCount": 2739,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2826&rangeEnd=2864",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2826&rangeEnd=2864"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_3_4166-4221",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4166-4221",
      "markText": "你可以不顾一切地拥有自己想要的人生，而不是由别人来决定。你仍有机会选择拥抱最真实的自我，而不是生活在别人眼中。",
      "totalCount": 2006,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4166&rangeEnd=4221",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4166&rangeEnd=4221"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_7_1888-1957",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1888-1957",
      "markText": "全心投入生活的真正核心在于：当下这一刻的价值感，既没有先决条件，也不是“当……时”。我们“现在”就值得拥有爱和归属感，此时此刻，如此而已。",
      "totalCount": 1926,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1888&rangeEnd=1957",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1888&rangeEnd=1957"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_4_5360-5459",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5360-5459",
      "markText": "坦露自己或许痛苦，但远不如我们用生命来躲避它来得痛苦；承认自己的弱点或许危险，但远不如我们放弃爱、归属感和喜悦来得危险——正是这些体验让我们变得脆弱不堪，但我们只有勇于探索黑暗，才能发现无限的光明。",
      "totalCount": 1830,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5360&rangeEnd=5459",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5360&rangeEnd=5459"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_6_4326-4424",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4326-4424",
      "markText": "当我们寻求他人的同情，那个人必须足够强大，懂得变通，更重要的是，他可以包容我们的优势和缺点。能与信任的人分享挫折，我们应该感到庆幸。当我们寻求安慰时，我们要学会在对的时间里找到对的人，倾诉对的事。",
      "totalCount": 1547,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4326&rangeEnd=4424",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4326&rangeEnd=4424"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_4_447-542",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "447-542",
      "markText": "早晨醒来，你会对自己说：“无论我已做到了什么，还有什么没有完成，我都觉得满足。”晚上临睡前，默念着：“我的确不完美，很脆弱，有时也会胆小，但这并不能改变我勇敢、值得被爱、拥有归属感的事实。”",
      "totalCount": 1010,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=447&rangeEnd=542",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=447&rangeEnd=542"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_6_13819-13857",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "13819-13857",
      "markText": "实践勇气、仁慈心和联结就是面对人生，看着周围的人，可以坦然地说：“我好累。”",
      "totalCount": 952,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13819&rangeEnd=13857",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13819&rangeEnd=13857"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_6_2562-2632",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2562-2632",
      "markText": "试图打动或说服这样的听众永远是一个错误，因为这意味着你要用真诚来交换别人的认可。千万不要指望用这种方式来体现你的价值，天啊，我是在白费工夫！",
      "totalCount": 924,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2562&rangeEnd=2632",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2562&rangeEnd=2632"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_6_6778-6808",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6778-6808",
      "markText": "当我表露自己内心的脆弱和失落时，我同样能看到自己身上的勇气。",
      "totalCount": 864,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6778&rangeEnd=6808",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6778&rangeEnd=6808"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_3_2232-2245",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2232-2245",
      "markText": "我们无法给予我们没有的东西",
      "totalCount": 832,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2232&rangeEnd=2245",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2232&rangeEnd=2245"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_3_607-651",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "607-651",
      "markText": "我总是中断写作去收拾屋子，花费大量的时间和金钱购置办公用品，然后整理它们。每次都是如此。",
      "totalCount": 816,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=607&rangeEnd=651",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=607&rangeEnd=651"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_3_2985-3089",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2985-3089",
      "markText": "也许最令我难以接受的教训是：数据清楚地显示，我们不能给予孩子我们没有的东西。当我们在人生旅途中能够全心生活，全力去爱，这远比依靠指导书来教育孩子更有说服力。",
      "totalCount": 768,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=860296&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2985&rangeEnd=3089",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/703325005d2088703a3a142?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2985&rangeEnd=3089"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "860296_3_1428-1472",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1428-1472",
      "markText": "确实，我们都在羞耻感中挣扎，担心自己不够完美。同样地，很多人都害怕被他人窥见真实的自我。",
